Package: currentTime
Type: Package
Title: Retrieves Current Time from Public NTP Servers in Pool.ntp.org
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Greg", "Hunt",
      email = "greg@firmansyah.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements an UDP NTP query to get a good approximation to the current time.   
    With the widespread use of NTP on hosts this is a somewhat anachronistic function. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: curl
